data.description: SELLER says bring ALL OFFERS! This meticulously designed home offers the epitome of Florida's coastal lifestyle, boasting direct boat/sailboat access and a stunning pool. As you approach your new residence, you will notice that the builder has paid meticulous attention to every facet. Upon entering the open-concept split-plan luxury home through the grand double wrought iron front doors, you are immediately captivated by the unobstructed, awe-inspiring view of the infinity pool, which gazes out over the tranquil canal. Designed with entertainment in mind, this home features 90-degree sliders that seamlessly connect to the expansive lanai, equipped with an outdoor kitchen, space for al fresco dining, and a convenient cabana bathroom. The chef's kitchen boasts a breakfast island, designer soft-close solid wood cabinetry, luxurious quartz countertops, and custom-tiled backsplash. The thoughtfully designed main suite provides a serene retreat, offering two walk-in closets and a luxurious walk-through shower, complemented by his and her vanities. Your new home features two guest bedrooms, a flexible study or den, crown molding, tray ceilings, solid core doors, and impact windows and doors for security. The resort-style pool offers a relaxing atmosphere, and the three-car garage provides ample storage.
